Home > Pet Friendly Hotels


Pet-Friendly Places







 Your pets are guests, too.

At Hotel Indigo, we’re used to welcoming guests with discerning tastes in music, design and food. Some of these guests often have more than two legs. That’s right – we’re a boutique hotel that happily welcomes four-legged furry friends with open arms and full bowls! When you stay at one of our properties, you can be sure that you won’t be the only one enjoying the world-class service that our knowledgeable staff offers. Each one of our hotels finds a fun and unique way to pamper you and your pet. From a welcome biscuit to their very own doggie bed, your pet will get a taste of the exclusive boutique experience that we have to offer at each one of our hotels.


Some of our hotels even have their very own permanent pet residences! Read below for some heart-warming tales about how our furry, fluffy and fishy friends can brighten your day and your stay when you book at select Hotel Indigo properties.

*This offer is valid at select hotels only.



 


































