                        Hotel Indigo Baton Rouge
                        From starring in musicals and hosting Lunch with Huey 
                        during Bring Your Pet to Work Week, this four-legged treasure 
                        is a local celebrity. Huey is adored by guests and staff alike 
                        thanks to his friendly, outgoing personality.






  Hotel Indigo Columbus Architectural Centre

  Miles can best be described as intuitive, sweet and 
  disciplined. This pooch knows the hotel schedule better 
  than some of the staff, and takes great care in making 
  sure that everyone feels welcomed at "his" hotel. 





                        Hotel Indigo New Orleans Garden District
                        These two are quite the pair! Rumored to have come 
                        from a long line of Siamese fighting fish, Rex and Zulu 
                        add a unique aesthetic to their surroundings while 
                        delighting guests with their unique, fishy personalities! 








  Hotel Indigo Atlanta Midtown
  A regular at Canine Cocktail Hour, this spunky Jack 
  Russell terrier was adopted from the Atlanta Humane 
  Society. Indie's sweet and fun personality adds a human 
  element to the hotel.































